'''七磷化铅'''是目前已知的[[铅|铅]]和[[磷|磷]]能形成的唯一二元磷化物，化学式为PbP<sub>7</sub>，其中含有[P<sub>7</sub>]<sup>2−</sup>[[原子簇|原子簇]]，该化合物在空气中稳定。<ref>Schäfer K, Benndorf C, Eckert H, et al. PbP<sub>7</sub> - a polyphosphide with a three-dimensional [P<sub>7</sub>]<sup>2−</sup> network of condensed and P-bridged P<sub>6</sub> hexagons[J]. Dalton Trans., 2014. 43(33): 12706-10</ref>
==晶体结构==
七磷化铅的[[晶胞参数|晶胞参数]]为：P2<sub>1</sub>/c，a＝970.70(11)，b＝673.34(10)，c＝1243.89(18) pm，β＝122.55(1)°，wR＝0.0488，2022 F<sup>2</sup>。磷原子簇中的每个磷原子和其余6个相连。

==制备及性质==
七磷化铅可由红磷和铅反应制得。它在{{convert|550|K|C}}时重新分解为单质。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=235|language=en|date=2016-03|pages=139–144|doi=10.1016/j.jssc.2015.12.028|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459615302942|title=2D 31 P solid state NMR spectroscopy, electronic structure and thermochemistry of PbP 7|accessdate=2019-05-28|author=Christopher Benndorf, Andrea Hohmann, Peer Schmidt, Hellmut Eckert, Dirk Johrendt, Konrad Schäfer, Rainer Pöttgen|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602023145/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459615302942|dead-url=no}}</ref>

